Usage:
    rake joybox:command

Commands:
    setup       # Setup a RubyMotion project to use Joybox
    generate    # Generates new classes for the proyect (Sprite, Scene & Layer)

Description:
    The 'rake joybox:setup' command modifies a new Ruby Motion project with 
    the necessary files and folders to start creating developing with Joybox.

    WARNING: The operation will delete your app_delegate.rb file, in case you 
    have any modification please do a backup before proceeding.

Example:
    rake joybox:setup

    This generates the folder structure of the project, app_delegate.rb and 
    copy the FPS image resources. 